googleReviewsBySlug.json.name: Martin Klinger
googleReviewsBySlug.json.text: Jeremy Lawson is the finest craftsman I know.  He is skillful and totally honest and his prices are very reasonable.  I once called him out to fix three different plumbing problems in three different rooms of my house.  I think that most plumbers would have worked on each of the problems until they were somewhat better.  Jeremy immediately realized that all three problems could be traced to the same cause: a bad water pressure regulator.  He checked the regulator, found that it had indeed failed, and replaced it.  That solved all three problems completely.  He is a terrific person to work with.
